---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Asparagus & Herby Mayo
description: This is crumbed chicken with a difference. First, it's coated with sweet mustard spice blend, then crumbed with crunchy
panko for delectable flavour and texture. Combine that with warmly spiced roasted veggies and a drizzle of herbed
mayo for a showstopper.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
